{{wikipedia}}

#[[Category:Seasonings]] Any [[green]], [[leaf]]y [[plant]], or [[part]]s thereof, used to [[flavour]] or [[season]] food.
#[[Plant]] whose [[root]]s, leaves or [[seed]]s, etc are used in [[medicine]].
#(''euphemistic slang'') [[Marijuana]].
#{{botany}} A plant whose [[stem]] is not [[woody]] and does not persist beyond each growing season

